name: Helping Spirit (free giveaway)
description:
We *need* each other to survive <3 

Artist's Note: dear NFT Community, this NFT was conceived to spread some hope in these surreal times and it was not intended for resale. In that spirit, it was priced at 0 (zero) to increase accessibility for all. Unfortunately HEN is not allowing me to set the royalties to 0. Kindly take 1 piece so others can take one as well, or if you take more, gift it to others to spread some kindness.
